{"tid":868492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★雙程證來港即買刀姦劫鳳姐 官斥可恥判囚8年","createTime":"2018-10-19T13:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T14:06:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b5e2f23aadba0e72e4e486187a6cb28e5c7a8d01","tid":868492,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T13:42:18.000Z","msg":"內地廚師去年9月以雙程證來港，抵港後即到上海街買開蠔刀，繼而佯裝嫖客光顧鳳姐，惟入房後即露出狼相，取出開蠔刀搶劫鳳姐，再邊吸毒邊將鳳姐強姦。廚師並迫鳳姐擺出誘人姿態拍裸照，以祼照威脅對方透露提款卡密碼。鳳姐慘遭凌辱達兩小時，最終赤身跑出單位求救。內地男今於高院承認搶劫、強姦、吸毒及勒索罪，法官直斥被告行為令人髮指，判囚8年。<br />\n祖籍湖北的被告胡昌雄（39歲）今透露與前妻育有一名兒子。被告警誡下聲稱，當日答應幫朋友帶手提電話回內地，以換取冰毒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181019/large/1539937117_7504.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181019%2Flarge%2F1539937117_7504.jpg&h=6d64c77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181019/58811397\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181019%2F58811397&d=hnmXpn6FTcVCC8%2BBwQ8Xxdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=79f5c9e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181019%2F58811397&h=a082f120\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181019/58811397</a>"},{"pid":"7a83cd0491cd0bdbecf316f3bb7e3359fc7eb216","tid":868492,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T13:42:42.000Z","msg":"專材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b039faa145237ff77265c01e23352de4d16144a","tid":868492,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T13:43:59.000Z","msg":"8年?<br />\n<br />\n一放監就成為香港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51093230185d5e5c50dfb29f5b0adf51da2d975e","tid":868492,"uid":32577,"like